 class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533343\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533343\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wgo1665702911332.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wgo1665702911332.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wgo1665702911332.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wgo1665702911332\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Foreign Key Cache\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wgo1665702911332__foreign_key_cache_135122\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">When the one entity is nested inside the many entity, Uniface uses a foreign key cache when retrieving the data.\n </p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"wgo1665702911332__fig_d43712e1_d43713e1_d43714e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Foreign entity</figcaption>\n<p class=\"p\">Department is a foreign entity:</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"wgo1665702911332__fig_w4302ab1b5b3b5b1_w4303ab1b5b3b5_w4304ab1b5b3_w4305ab1b5_w4306ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Foreign entity in form\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/foreignentity.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wgo1665702911332__p_d43715e1_d43716e1_d43717e1\">Before generating a Select on a foreign key when fetching an occurrence of the many entity into the component, Uniface first checks the foreign key cache to see if the data for the foreign entity is already present in the component. This can greatly improve performance if the user retrieves multiple occurrences of the outermost entity for which the foreign key does not change.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wgo1665702911332__p_d43718e1_d43719e1_d43720e1\">For example, if you retrieve PERSON occurrences with a foreign key link to DEPARTMENT, for people located in the same department as the previously fetched one, the Select for the DEPARTMENT data comes from the foreign key cache, instead of from the database.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wgo1665702911332__p_d43721e1_d43722e1_d43723e1\">A Select operation from cache is much faster than going to the database. The foreign key cache is completely automatic.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gpk1665702926045.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Format of Overflow Tables</a><p>Uniface overflow tables are in a format that only Uniface can understand. If you use a non-Uniface product to access the data, the product must be configured to understand overflow tables.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533343\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533343\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Foreign Key Cache Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Foreign Key Cache When the one entity is nested inside the many entity, Uniface uses a foreign key cache when retrieving the data. Figure 1. Foreign entity Department is a foreign entity: Before generating a Select on a foreign key when fetching an occurrence of the many entity into the component, Uniface first checks the foreign key cache to see if the data for the foreign entity is already present in the component. This can greatly improve performance if the user retrieves multiple occurrences of the outermost entity for which the foreign key does not change. For example, if you retrieve PERSON occurrences with a foreign key link to DEPARTMENT, for people located in the same department as the previously fetched one, the Select for the DEPARTMENT data comes from the foreign key cache, instead of from the database. A Select operation from cache is much faster than going to the database. The foreign key cache is completely automatic. Related Links Format of Overflow Tables Uniface overflow tables are in a format that only Uniface can understand. If you use a non-Uniface product to access the data, the product must be configured to understand overflow tables. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}